                Build your best community starting from here.
            </h1>
            <p class="text-silver text-balance">
                Meet and communicate with the best people to run projects,
                events or other activities in a more effective and fun way
            </p>
            <article class="flex gap-4 w-full max-w-[350px]">
                <a
                    class="w-full py-2 text-center rounded-xl bg-cerise text-white inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-bl-none"
                    href="#">Explore</a
                >
                <a
                    class="w-full py-1 rounded-md bg-primar inline-flex justify-center items-center"
